{"tid":1487192,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"whatsapp有份聲稱統計818遊行嘅survey伏伏地，求FC","createTime":"2019-08-19T07:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T21:40:51.000Z","uid":31019,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41a54eecfa035d5eca3e11f5574b2edc7e5cd2e1","tid":1487192,"uid":31019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"whatsapp收到內容如下，仲要留個人資料，感覺伏伏地，有冇人可以fc下？<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n急，請幫忙轉發：<br />\n<br />\n☀由於在民陣網頁中看到昨天818維園集因擬參與之人數太多，很多市民反映未能成功排隊進入維園內🤦🏻&zwj;♂🤦🏻&zwj;♀，以令民陣最後公佈人數為170萬，但按現場人士目測，認為實際應多於616之二百萬(+1)之數目。<br />\n<br />\n鑒於想還昨天每一位熱心參與的市民一個公道，不會因入不到維園而徒勞無功，同時更想令一眾冷血當權者，可更清晰認真聽到香港當下洶湧群情的怒吼之聲，現懇請各位幫忙填寫以下問卷（只有一條問題）：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"HTTPS://www.surveymonkey.com/r/6F7933M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=HTTPS%3A%2F%2Fwww.surveymonkey.com%2Fr%2F6F7933M&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46yukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=d95c87af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">HTTPS://www.surveymonkey.com/r/6F7933M</a><br />\n<br />\n🌟截止時間為8.19日晚上12:00<br />\n<br />\n無論你昨天能否成功進入維園參加集會，或只能在附近街上遊走，也懇求協助答一答這問題，有關結果將會交予民陣參考，期望可讓其估算出更實際的數字！(因需了解可進入維園，與不能進入維園的參與者比例，所以無論你是成功入內，或是只能在外邊遊走者，也懇請填寫，感激不盡！）<br />\n<br />\n註：引述梁家傑律師所說，這集會已有不反對通知書，是合法舉行的，因此如昨天擬前往參加集會的時候在街上排隊等入維園，或在離開時走在街上均不會屬於違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n另，問卷受訪者之資料將會絕對保密（包括閣下的手機或電腦IP資料也絕不會被記錄），有關資料將會在完成統計後銷燒，再次感謝各位幫忙！🙇🏻&zwj;♂🙇🏻&zwj;♀"},{"pid":"b14a0d3187fe3b9b27e5da953b37d8b792c69c6e","tid":1487192,"uid":17378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"同求fc, 推"},{"pid":"f31bc9bf8ad56f60b2e174f51cacf7e54aeca772","tid":1487192,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"之前有一份係和理非是否支持升級調查<br />\n都係勁伏<br />\n唔好填"},{"pid":"8721cee37bc5927b92e6315df9d47f5021895dc8","tid":1487192,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2af5af7b7e9753e1aebda437b7c6115fc1718eed","tid":1487192,"uid":265434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"但入去睇其實只需要填一條問題咋喎"},{"pid":"7693d38f23cf8ad776e77a756a0ee411eaa55b6a","tid":1487192,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:21:43.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c26a82af6167db3de96d95966b1a5978f031076d","tid":1487192,"uid":32753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"冇伏既<br />\n但唔明點解要咁點人數<br />\n冇參考意義"},{"pid":"d29074d40b92c52bf8dbf80cf5d0547d56a30e08","tid":1487192,"uid":209318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"170呢個人數上哂新聞啦"},{"pid":"4e6f5b1506dcf020f951de09ee6270c516c1516b","tid":1487192,"uid":179120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"唔知咩人整，但得一條問題應該冇野？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpUuX45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpUuX45.png&h=a3c8d588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1CTFiD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1CTFiD.png&h=916ebfac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"096a3d3eda0fa4e8803eaf7acaca03afe1f36a91","tid":1487192,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"政府啲on9又比位人入啦"},{"pid":"9bda22cfcaef1c2cd3c9a529ff86e9f284418807","tid":1487192,"uid":203615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T21:40:51.000Z","msg":"三哥 幾時有新故 好掛住隻husky<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}